deck: One adventure as The Black Fury then off with the mask.
description:
Origin

Rex King is an adventure who is befriended in Borneo by a black panther whom he calls Kato; after King devises a costume he and Kato take down people exploiting the natives.

In his second adventure Rex King and the panther, now called Jet, continue their exploits in the Far East, only now he does it without the costume and is known as Rex King Adventurer.

Creators

No one knows who created Rex King, however his career as Black Fury didn’t last long, their already being two other characters by that name, to say nothing about the use of the name Kato. So after their first adventure they become the uncostumed Rex King and Jet.

deck: Ben is a bee from the Westland (a part of the Netherlands which is famous for the greenhouses).
description:
Origin

Ben is a bee from the Westland, a part in the west of the Netherlands, where there's many greenhouses. He has adapted himself to life amongst the greenhouses and its many inhabitants. He has painted himself green and white, the colors of the Westland. Except on Christmas, then he paints himself red and white.

Creation

Ben was created by independent creator Richard de Rijke. In 2015, when he was asked what he missed in the local newspaper "Groot Westland" (Great Westland), he responded that he missed a comic strip. The people around him thought it was a great idea and said he should do it. Though that wasn't his initial goal, he thought about what would make a great comic strip. He decided on a bee, which is very common in the greenhouses of the Westland.

Ben can be seen in the weekly newspaper "Groot Westland" and on his own Facebook page.

Powers & Abilities

Like every bee, Ben can fly. When he flies among the greenhouses, he adjusts his flight pattern. He also likes to ride a bike on top of the greenhouses.
name: Ben, de Westlandse Bij
